Invocation Name: human body trivia
des: Test your knowledge of the human body by taking our fun human body quiz. The human body is an amazing structure which contains a wide range of complex parts and processes. Do you know about the body’s important organs, digestive processes and brain functions? Learn more about the anatomy of the human body as well as parts such as the heart, bones, eyes, skin, muscles, skeleton, ears and nose. Answer all questions and repeat the game. This skill is fun and challenging for everyone!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
